The paper focuses on deep metric learning for image clustering and retrieval tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The proposed method also involves distance metric learning, which is relevant to multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new metric for measuring similarity between image pairs, which is related to artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
